{"tid":2032914,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怪得商鋪一有黑警來到就落閘啦","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T10:37:55.000Z","uid":214007,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bcfb3336a9dd2743dbfa4a29af9ffd27684c297a","tid":2032914,"uid":214007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:26:37.000Z","msg":"仲開鋪容乜易成間鋪D野都俾人徵用哂啊"},{"pid":"d7baf4b6634555c0a35848ca44f21ccbb9d2679d","tid":2032914,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"分分鍾連老闆娘都比黑警用埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登紅色五毛分化警告</span><br />\n宜家班死五毛<span style=\"color: red;\">除左用鬥黃進行分化，仲用扮演移民/留守派黎進行分化</span>，大家請保持獨立思考<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後大家要幫手簽個聯署支持BNO平權救手足</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=95ea2b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"5d3d3e8992cacffc91af7b65bb06795971c3e0e4","tid":2032914,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"香港黑警， 快d 自殺死"}]}